frequency of 1,000 Hz (ECG) and 100 Hz (ACC). Each PPG signal includes
annotation of quality and reference HR. PPG signal quality is indicated
binary: 1 indicates good quality for HR estimation, 0 indicates signals where
HR cannot be detected reliably and thus these signals are unsuitable for any
analysis.},
